19:37.259 --> 19:38.510
Coffey to ﬁeld it,

19:38.552 --> 19:41.715
but Martinez is safely aboard
with a single to left
to start off...

19:41.806 --> 19:46.926
SARAH, I think
this is the beginning
of a beautiful friendship.

