Kevin! Brian!
Rise and shine,
sleepyheads.

19:53.693 --> 19:56.025
You're gonna be
late for school.

19:59.949 --> 20:01.655
Hey, guys, it's time...

20:05.788 --> 20:06.948
Kevin?

20:13.754 --> 20:16.245
Kevin, sweetie, come here.

20:18.050 --> 20:20.041
Did you have a bad dream?

20:36.569 --> 20:37.900
(ALARM RINGING)
SARAH: Time to get up!

20:37.987 --> 20:39.443
(CLUB MUSIC PLAYING)

20:39.530 --> 20:40.485
What?

20:40.573 --> 20:43.064
You had 837 hours’ sleep.

20:43.159 --> 20:46.777
Yeah, well, that's...
Why are you yelling at me?

20:46.871 --> 20:48.736
Am I talking loud?
Yes!

